        "paragraph_index": 0,
        "text": "## Ligands with More Than 6 Reported pKa Values in SRD-46\n\nYes! There are **two ligands** in the NIST SRD-46 database that have more than 6 distinct reported pKa values:\n\n| Ligand ID | Ligand Name | Common Abbreviation | Distinct pKa Steps |\n|-----------|-------------|---------------------|------------------:|\n| ligand_6356 | Diethylenetrinitrilopentaacetic acid | **DTPA** | 8 |\n| ligand_8412 | Nitrilotris(methylenephosphonic acid) | **NTP** | 7 |",
